{"tid":2227095,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美國多家巨頭宣布裁員！！","createTime":"2020-10-02T13:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T15:47:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"65cf74079b02b83430657e4c68d1a982b43f25d2","tid":2227095,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"美國多家巨頭宣布裁員。迪士尼（DISNEY）9月29日表示，由於加利福尼亞州主題公園長期關閉，迪士尼將裁員28,000人。美國化工品牌陶氏公司（Dow Chemical Company）也宣布將削減6%的人力成本，但沒有披露具體的裁員數字。美國第二大煉油公司馬拉松石油（MRO）也於日前宣布，將在公司內展開廣泛裁員，馬拉松石油已經於8月起關閉加利福尼亞州和新墨西哥州的煉油廠，目前已經裁員800人。<br />\n<br />\n著名服裝品牌Ralph Lauren宣布在全球裁員15%。國防和航空航天巨頭雷神技術公司（Raytheon Technologies）宣布裁員1.5萬人。截至9月16日，紐約古根海姆博物館已解僱了11%的員工。美國零售巨頭柯爾百貨（Kohl『s）正在裁員15%。戴爾公司（Dell）9月14日通知員工將裁員以削減成本，但具體數量不明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/530977/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E7%A9%86%E8%BF%AA%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%B7%9E%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F530977%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F-%25E7%25A9%2586%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%25B7%259E%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25B2%25B8%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmdnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=b26dc874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/530977/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E7%A9%86%E8%BF%AA%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%B7%9E%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%A8%E9%